{
  "id": "RAW_fce7e794",
  "title": "Google Skills: 您学习 Google AI 及更多内容的新平台",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwODY4OTk2Mg==&mid=2652159921&idx=2&sn=a3a0a44918b7f7844dea7acc15eb9392",
  "date": "2025-11-07 09:33:00",
  "author": "谷歌开发者",
  "siteName": "谷歌开发者",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\">帮助每个人获得他们所需要的 AI 学习资源，包括我们那些正在寻找熟练开发者的 Google Cloud 客户。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 1.8;padding-right: 5px;padding-left: 5px;max-width: 100%;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhn7k66q8m3\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhn7k67aj6l\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\">以下文章来源于谷歌云服务，作者 Google Cloud</span></span></span></p>\n       <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"谷歌云服务\" data-alias=\"Google_Cloud_China\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/o20ft1Bw6gW1mnNIibxK0iaYX5LBvN9ickicV55PPC9rICRH4A31qmlWmzc9hJdsfRMrLZ30mfxuwh9iccn0iatLcpUA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"Google Cloud 为企业上云带来全新方式，提供 AI、基础架构、开发者支持、数据处理、安全与协作等工具，助力企业应对当今与未来的挑战。目前已有超过 200 个国家和地区的客户选择 Google Cloud 作为他们所信赖的合作伙伴。\" data-id=\"MzkwMTMwNTIxMQ==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"2\" data-verify_status=\"2\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n       <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n        <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 1.8;padding-right: 5px;padding-left: 5px;max-width: 100%;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 4 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 1.8;padding-right: 5px;padding-left: 5px;max-width: 100%;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n           <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-imgfileid=\"100014282\" data-ratio=\"0.4925925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a9dacdf6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fmmecoa_png%2Fo20ft1Bw6gVcl6QUibAszibTrGkhBmuKXeaebKRQHDBxwchRL3icibqkibFtgH36iarAPEdSFIPqHFtMPY9EoTSVNgqQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D0\"></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"border-left: 3px solid rgb(66, 133, 244);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;padding-left: 8px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n           <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Erin Rifkin</span></strong></p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n         <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n            <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Google Cloud 学习部门，董事总经理</span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:24px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:100%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">从课堂到职场，当今世界的工作方式正以惊人的速度变化。随着 AI 和云计算的飞速发展，我们不仅需要适应，更需要探索强大的新途径来茁壮成长，无论您身居何职。</span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: unset;padding-right: 5px;padding-left: 5px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"text-align: left;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了帮助每个人紧跟步伐，我们在近期推出&nbsp;<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkwMTMwNTIxMQ==&amp;mid=2247497804&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=62c248da38bd97d2109860e2a12602b5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">Gemini Enterprise</a>&nbsp;的同时，宣布了对学习项目进行三项重大更新。</span></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"flex-flow: row;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;flex-direction: row;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;margin-left: 4px;margin-right: 3px;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"border-left: 1px solid rgb(66, 133, 244);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;padding: 13px;height: auto;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <div style=\"text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-left: 0px solid rgb(62, 62, 62);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;background-color: rgba(241, 238, 238, 0.41);padding: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n             <div style=\"max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n              <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个全新的平台，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Google Skills</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;将把近 3,000 个课程和实验集中于一处 - 包括来自 Google Cloud、Google DeepMind、Grow with Google 和 Google for Education 的内容。</span></p>\n             </div>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"flex-flow: row;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;flex-direction: row;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;margin-left: 4px;margin-right: 3px;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"border-left: 1px solid rgb(66, 133, 244);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;padding: 13px;height: auto;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-left: 0px solid rgb(62, 62, 62);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;background-color: rgba(241, 238, 238, 0.41);padding: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一项新计划，即&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini Enterprise Agent Ready (GEAR) 计划</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，旨在赋能百万开发者使用我们新的 Gemini Enterprise 平台构建企业级 AI 智能体。</span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"flex-flow: row;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;flex-direction: row;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;margin-left: 4px;margin-right: 3px;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"border-left: 1px solid rgb(66, 133, 244);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;padding: 13px;height: auto;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-left: 0px solid rgb(62, 62, 62);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;background-color: rgba(241, 238, 238, 0.41);padding: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">与金融服务公司 Jack Henry 建立合作伙伴关系，作为我们基于技能的招聘计划的一部分，帮助快速招聘技术人才。</span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;padding: 0px 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过这些更新，我们正在履行我们的承诺，帮助每个人获得他们所需要的 AI 学习资源，包括我们那些正在寻找熟练开发者的 Google Cloud 客户。</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: center;max-width: 100%;padding: 0px 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-top: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 85%;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"max-width: 100%;transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(251, 188, 4);max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"white-space-collapse: collapse;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Google Cloud 学习者、客户和合作伙</span></span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">伴在 Google Skills 上可以获得哪些</span></span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">新功能？</span></span></strong></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;padding: 0px 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了支持从学生到开发者再到高管等不同技能水平的人群，我们推出了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Google Skills</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。这个全新的学习平台旨在帮助人们培养在当今职场中取得成功所需的技能，并帮助企业找到并培养他们蓬勃发展所需的人才。仅在去年一年，人们就完成了超过&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2,600 万门</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">课程、实验和证书——现在，它们都汇聚于此。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了来自 Google 各部门的所有内容 (例如 Google DeepMind 的新 AI 研究课程) 之外，此次发布还为 Google Cloud 客户带来了一系列新内容，使他们始终处于 AI 技能构建的前沿:</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 93%;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 15px;background-color: rgba(52, 168, 83, 0.11);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"letter-spacing:1px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n            <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini Code Assist:&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 驱动的学习和新技能徽章</span></strong></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;padding: 0px 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini Code Assist 将帮助工程师、开发者、数据科学家等无需离开 Google Skills 平台即可使用 Gemini 轻松进行编码。该功能已在 20 多个动手实验中启用，并将在未来成为所有相关实验的一部分。开发者还可以通过获得新的技能徽章来证明其 Gemini Code Assist 技能：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用 Gemini Code Assist 快速启动应用程序开发。</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们还顺应了 \"vibe 编程\" 的潮流，为应用开发者推出了两个全新的技能徽章:</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;background-color: rgba(52, 168, 83, 0.15);align-self: center;padding: 5px 26px 5px 25px;margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用 Vibe Coding 和 MCP 构建智能云应用</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-style: dashed;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 1px;border-left-color: rgb(52, 168, 83);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 7px;padding: 7px 21px 21px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgba(254, 255, 255, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">旨在帮助开发者掌握模型上下文协议 (MCP) 服务器开发和 Google Cloud 上 vibe 编程的基础知识及实践技能。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;background-color: rgba(52, 168, 83, 0.15);align-self: center;padding: 5px 26px 5px 25px;margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用智能体开发工具包 (ADK) 部署智能体</span></span></strong></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-style: dashed;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 1px;border-left-color: rgb(52, 168, 83);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 7px;padding: 7px 21px 21px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">则使开发者能够使用模型上下文协议 (MCP)、Agent-to-Agent 协议 (A2A) 和智能体开发工具包 (ADK) 等常用方法，构建先进的 AI 系统，使不同的 AI 组件能够顺畅协作。</span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 93%;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 15px;background-color: rgba(52, 168, 83, 0.11);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"letter-spacing:1px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n            <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为 Google Cloud 客户和组织提供更好的体验</span></strong></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;padding: 0px 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">您提出的需求，我们会倾听。作为 Google Skills 的一部分，我们保留了 Google Cloud Skills Boost 的精华，同时在全新 Google Skills 平台上添加了您一直期待的功能。例如，Google Cloud 客户将可以继续免费访问整个 Google Cloud 内容库，现在还包含来自 Google DeepMind 的新内容。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们还新增了一项功能，让您可以为您的团队分配最相关的课程和动手实验。这种个性化设置不仅有利于您的业务发展，更能加速您团队的创新能力。</span></p>\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，您现在可以使用专为您的组织定制的公司排行榜，激发良性竞争并增添乐趣。最后，对于 Google Skills 管理员，我们将添加更多功能，使报告功能更加高级。这意味着您可以获得更多数据、更高灵活性和更深入的洞察，实时跟踪团队的进度。</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 93%;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 15px;background-color: rgba(52, 168, 83, 0.11);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"letter-spacing:1px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n            <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">云学习从未如此有趣: 全新的游戏化功能</span></strong></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;padding: 0px 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于组织来说，Google Skills 使团队更容易保持参与度和更新知识。这一点至关重要: 74% 的决策者认同技术学习资源能够提高员工的工作效率，71% 的组织在使用这些资源后实现了收入增长。</span><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></sup><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;换句话说，更多的学习机会对企业而言是普遍的福音。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">但仅仅学习是不够的。学习需要充满乐趣、引人入胜，并且易于融入你的日程安排。因此，我们为 Google Skills 带来了全新的 AI 驱动和游戏化功能，旨在提升学习效率。</span></p>\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">游戏化功能：</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;background-color: rgba(52, 168, 83, 0.15);align-self: center;padding: 5px 26px 5px 25px;margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">联赛 (Leagues)</span></strong></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-style: dashed;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 1px;border-left-color: rgb(52, 168, 83);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 7px;padding: 7px 21px 21px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgba(254, 255, 255, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用此仪表板小部件，鼓励基于获得的积分进行良性竞争。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;background-color: rgba(52, 168, 83, 0.15);align-self: center;padding: 5px 26px 5px 25px;margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">成就 (Achievements)</span></span></strong></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-style: dashed;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 1px;border-left-color: rgb(52, 168, 83);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 7px;padding: 7px 21px 21px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgba(254, 255, 255, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过新的视觉效果和便捷的社交分享选项，庆祝您的学习里程碑。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;background-color: rgba(52, 168, 83, 0.15);align-self: center;padding: 5px 26px 5px 25px;margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">持续学习 (Learning streaks)</span></span></strong></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-style: dashed;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 1px;border-left-color: rgb(52, 168, 83);height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px 7px;padding: 7px 21px 21px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgba(254, 255, 255, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过奖励积分和 \"冻结连续记录\" 来培养持续的学习习惯。</span></span></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 93%;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 15px;background-color: rgba(52, 168, 83, 0.11);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"letter-spacing:1px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n            <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">GEAR: 赋能百万开发者的新冲刺计划</span></strong></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;padding: 0px 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们还宣布推出&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 168, 83);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini Enterprise 智能体就绪 (Gemini Enterprise Agent Ready, GEAR) 计划</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，这是一项全新的教育冲刺计划，旨在赋能百万开发者使用我们全新的智能体平台 Gemini Enterprise。通过群组式学习模式，帮助他们构建、部署和管理智能体。作为 GEAR 的一部分，开发者可以通过 Google Skills 获得技能徽章。</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-top: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 10%;height: auto;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"max-width: 100%;transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"white-space-collapse: collapse;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">直通就业途径: 更快捷的招聘方式</span></strong></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;max-width: 100%;padding: 0px 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">培养技能不仅有利于个人职业发展，也有利于企业发展。正因如此，我们推出了 Google Skills，帮助人们更轻松地获得雇主所需的技能，并帮助企业找到成功所需的人才。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们宣布，对于在美国完成 Google Cloud 网络安全或数据分析证书的学员，将有机会直接获得领先金融服务公司 Jack Henry 的面试机会。您将有机会完成模拟公司真实场景的定制化动手实验。这些实验是公司招聘流程的第一步，让您能够切实展示技能，获得新的工作机会。我们期待未来将此模式推广至更多 Google Cloud 客户。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 95%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;padding: 20px;background-repeat: repeat;background-attachment: scroll;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 8px;border-style: dashed;border-color: rgb(66, 133, 244);overflow: hidden;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251107124617_06460b&quot;);background-position: 0% 0% !important;background-size: 18.7837% !important;\" class=\"wx_imgbc_placeholder\">\n         <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"text-align: justify;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"我们很高兴能与 Google Cloud 合作，共同重塑人才招聘。通过利用 Google Cloud 证书，我们能够更有效地识别和招募顶尖人才，从而推动我们的发展，填补关键的技能缺口。\"</span></p>\n           <p style=\"text-align: right;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">——Jack Henry 首席招聘官 Holly Novak</span></strong></span></p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;max-width: 100%;padding: 0px 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一举措尤为重要，因为企业正在积极寻找人才。最近的一项研究发现，82% 的企业更愿意招聘和雇用拥有这些资质的专业人士。</span><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们才刚刚开始。无论您是想求职的个人，还是希望提升团队技能的企业领导者，在这个全新的 AI 世界中，每个人都能找到属于自己的发展机遇。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(169, 169, 169);padding: 0px 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 6px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 9px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">1&nbsp;</span></sup><span leaf=\"\">Google/Ipsos，Cloud Learning Services Market Pulse，定量部分于 2024 年 9 月至 10 月进行调查，定性部分于 2024 年 10 月至 11 月进行调查，（美国、英国、法国、德国、印度、巴西、墨西哥、日本、澳大利亚/新西兰）</span></p>\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 9px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2</span></sup><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Google/Ipsos，Cloud Learning Services Market Pulse，定量部分于 2024 年 9 月至 10 月进行调查，定性部分于 2024 年 10 月至 11 月进行调查，（美国、英国、法国、德国、印度、巴西、墨西哥、日本、澳大利亚/新西兰）</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google 推出全新整合式 AI 学习平台 Google Skills，涵盖近 3000 门课程和实验，并发布 Gemini Enterprise Agent Ready 计划和就业合作，助力开发者掌握 AI 技能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google 推出全新整合式 AI 学习平台 Google Skills，涵盖近 3000 门课程和实验，并发布 Gemini Enterprise Agent Ready 计划和就业合作，助力开发者掌握 AI 技能。",
